20
00:02:40,166 --> 00:02:41,916
DESPITE BEING IN THE OUTLANDS,

21
00:02:42,000 --> 00:02:43,916
IT CAN BE SAID THAT
THE REVOLUTION CURRENTLY

22
00:02:44,000 --> 00:02:47,458
TAKING PLACE ON THE WORLD,
