00:21:59,250 --> 00:22:02,041
- COMMUNICATIONS FOR BOTH
THE 606 AND THE 808,

397
00:22:02,125 --> 00:22:04,541
INDICATE THERE ARE NO
ENEMY SHIPS IN OUR AREA.

